text: Anadolu Kartalları (Anatolian Eagles) is a 2011 Turkish romantic adventure drama movie directed by Ömer Vargı and starring Engin Altan Düzyatan, Çağatay Ulusoy, Özge Özpirinçci, Hande Subaşı, Ekin Türkmen. ==Other websites== * Category:2011 romantic drama movies Category:2011 adventure movies Category:Turkish movies Category:Turkish-language movies Category:Movies directed by Ömer Vargı Category:Movies about aviation Category:Movies about air forces Category:Movies set in Turkey
title: Anadolu Kartalları
